 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2013:289
 http://www.mandriva.com/en/support/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : owncloud
 Date    : December 17, 2013
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated owncloud package fixes security vulnerability:
 
 Possible security bypass on admin page under certain circumstances
 and MariaDB (CVE-2013-6403).
 
 The owncloud package has been updated to version 5.0.13, fixing this
 and many other issues.
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2013-6403
 http://advisories.mageia.org/MGASA-2013-0367.html
